OL,7,FPolice said they have received reports
OL,8,Ffrom more than 70 people as
OL,9,Finvestigations continue into
OL,10,Fallegations of missing ashes and
OL,11,Ffuneral plan fraud at a former funeral
OL,12,Fdirectors.
OL,14,FOperation Koine was launched in April
OL,15,Flast year following reports relating
OL,16,Fto the practices of the former A Milne
OL,17,FIndependent Funeral Directors in the
OL,18,FGlasgow and Dumbarton areas.
