OL,4,Cdirectors receive reports from dozens
OL,5,Cof people
OL,7,FPolice said they have received reports
OL,8,Ffrom more than 70 people but believe a
OL,9,Flarger number may be affected and
OL,10,Furged anyone in that position to
OL,11,Fcontact them.
OL,13,FDetective Superintendent Robert Bowie
OL,14,Fsaid: "This is an unprecedented
OL,15,Finvestigation for Police Scotland and
OL,16,Fone of the largest ongoing financial
OL,17,Finquiries.
OL,19,F"I want to reassure the public, we
OL,20,Fhave a dedicated team working through
OL,21,Fhundreds of lines of inquiry.
