OL,7,F"Although the work we're doing may not
OL,8,Fbe visible, we are committed to fully
OL,9,Finvestigating."
OL,11,FMr Bowie said the "vast majority" of
OL,12,Fcomplaints relate to alleged
OL,13,Ffraudulent prepaid funeral plans.
OL,15,FHe said most cremated remains
OL,16,Frecovered from previous A Milne
OL,17,Fpremises have been returned to
OL,18,Ffamilies but a "small amount" remain
OL,19,Funclaimed.
