OL,7,FThe detective said: "In terms of some
OL,8,Fof the cremated remains which had been
OL,9,Frecovered at previous premises used by
OL,10,FA Milne independent funeral directors,
OL,11,Fwe have been able to return the vast
OL,12,Fmajority of those cremated remains to
OL,13,Ffamily members or deal with them in
OL,14,Fterms of their family's wishes.
OL,16,F"As it stands, there is still a small
OL,17,Famount of cremated remains which
OL,18,Fremain unclaimed and unidentified, and
OL,19,Fthat's what we're looking to achieve
OL,20,Fthrough traditional lines of inquiry."
