OL,4,Cdirectors receive reports from dozens
OL,5,Cof people
OL,7,FSpecialist officers, including from
OL,8,Fthe Financial Investigations Unit, are
OL,9,Finvolved in the investigation.
OL,11,FKate Wallace, chief executive of
OL,12,FVictim Support Scotland, said:
OL,13,F"Finding out that your loved one may
OL,14,Fnot have been cared for in the way
OL,15,Fthey would have wanted following their
OL,16,Fdeath is extremely upsetting and
OL,17,Fshocking.
